comments.body: Quote from: goldlyre on December 09, 2023, 02:19:11 PMIs the blue slabs of Anacs any special than the yellows?The jungle green slabs were only used for a few months by ANACS while they transitioned from the yellow to the white/light ones (that were the last ones used for physical cryptos)It is definitely more rare, but some collectors prefer the "original" yellow slabs.Just depends what you like to collect.
